Ordering system and delivery are terrible. 1) No option for contactless delivery with their online system. Their driver will show up at the door asking you to sign the credit card slip. This last time, delivery guy was masked but had it pulled down (nose commando) standing two feet in front of me asking to sign. 2) Twice now when ordering online they messed up the delivery address. This last time I ordered at 6:05 and waited... and waited. Called an hour and five minutes later at 7:10 to check on status. Was told by the guy they were really busy and the delivery driver was on the way. At 7:20 I received a call from the driver asking me which town I was in. He said it wasn't on the slip. I guess he was driving around in the wrong town for a while? Finally showed up about fifteen minutes later, nose commando, with a cold pizza.  Needless to say we will not be ordering from them again.
